Project Rules

Backend must always use Laravel (latest stable version).

Frontend must always use Vue.js with Vite.

Backend and frontend are separated but live in the same project and communicate strictly via API (SPA architecture).

Database must always be MySQL.

The entire project must run through Docker (nginx, php-fpm, mysql, node).

All database changes must use Laravel migrations.

Follow the provided design exactly.

Keep the code clean, modular, and production-ready.
